{"itemid":1512,"subject":"More on the Worldbook","event":"Here&#39;s another piece I did on THE WORLD OF ICE AND FIRE, this one taped in the UK during my last trip over there.\r\n\r\n\r\n<lj-embed id=\"504\" />\r\n\r\nI also did a much longer interview with my editor Anne Groell for the US edition of the worldbook.&nbsp; That one is coming up on line as well, though it seems to have been divided into smaller segments.\r\n\r\n<lj-embed id=\"505\" />\r\n\r\n<lj-embed id=\"506\" />\r\n\r\nMore of that to come, I am sure.\r\n\r\nAnd here&#39;s another of the interviews I did in New York on my latest trip, this one a sit down with Christopher Farley of WALL STREET JOURNAL that covers considerably more ground than just the worldbook.\r\n\r\n<lj-embed id=\"507\" />\r\n\r\nEnjoy.","ditemid":387157,"eventtime":"2014-11-01 11:50:00","props":{"current_mood":"happy","current_location":"Santa Fe","taglist":"voyager, world of ice and fire","current_moodid":15,"commentalter":1415379176,"crosspost_tw":"More on the Worldbook http://j.mp/1u83nWX","opt_lockcomments":1,"picture_keyword":"flames","opt_screening":"F","personifi_tags":"nterms:yes","revnum":1,"interface":"web","revtime":1415856568},"can_comment":0,"logtime":"2014-11-01 17:49:44","anum":85,"url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/387157.html","event_timestamp":1414842600,"reply_count":10,"comments":[{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/124186734/72810108","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/387157.html?thread=19688533#t19688533","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/387157.html?thread=19688533#t19688533","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/387157.html?thread=19688533#t19688533","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"ext_2851204","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"https://www.facebook.com/lrock3","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":19688533,